Is this what heaven is like, or maybe hell, to witness everything that you are missing out on.   Then you look at your other lives, those that lived before you, have they had to watch your just concluded life? You think back on the things you did in your life, the things you did when you thought no one was watching.   You were the worst, you realize now, well, maybe not the worst, but that is how you feel when you think of those dirty little secrets.  But, was is the purpose of this? Is this just some cruel joke? Or is this the way you are supposed to learn from your mistakes. Or, perhaps, you are being prepared to live this next
